MIME media type name : Application

MIME subtype name : Vendor Tree - vnd.ms-windows.wsd.oob

Required parameters : N/A

Optional parameters : 
N/A

Encoding considerations : binary


Security considerations : 
The content of this media type consists of printer pairing data.
This media type contains no executable content. The media type is used as
part of network printer installation, specifically the Tap and Setup and
Tap and Reconnect use cases. This media type does not itself provide
confidentiality or integrity protection.

Interoperability considerations : 
N/A

https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/hardware/dn481542(v=vs.85).aspx
